{"tid":2490441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駱惠寧: 維護國家安全 就是破壞香港繁榮發展","createTime":"2021-04-15T14:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T15:24:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":121,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"b3c348194e36b4438faea3de4a3acd79d4e9c033","tid":2490441,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"駱惠寧口誤「維護」國安是破壞繁榮<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦主任駱惠寧在政府舉辦的全民國家安全教育日上致詞時，呼籲社會參與維護國家安全，但口誤說要「更廣泛凝聚維護國家安全、就是破壞香港繁榮發展損害市民利益福祉的共識」。<br />\n<br />\n據中聯辦網頁，駱惠寧應是指要「危害」國家安全就是破壞香港繁榮發展，兩者剛好對調。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1382603872535908352\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1382603872535908352&d=Uh5SjXth0XRRLWSKrhPNwIdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=c1e7637a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhkcnews_com%2Fstatus%2F1382603872535908352&h=b9d3d8b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hkcnews_com/status/1382603872535908352</a>"},{"pid":"0243e5aaaa0b94c03540810f5d8ea200d038f541","tid":2490441,"uid":42188,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"有講錯到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f87f4c0f14002a79952d2c6144edb6807b50b0d","tid":2490441,"uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0243e5aaaa0b94c03540810f5d8ea200d038f541","tid":2490441,"uid":42188,"like":72,"dislike":0,"score":72,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T14:59:56.000Z","msg":"有講錯到咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-15T15:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img 